{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":76020,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"书 院","timestamp":1593750552,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":76029,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"建议把“旧学校”取消了，恢复工农兵大学生","timestamp":1593750613,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":76035,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"去发给邱宝","timestamp":1593750690,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":76039,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那你可以不上学，去深山老林里种地，没人剥削你","timestamp":1593750741,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":76042,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"打政治相关tag啊","timestamp":1593750815,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":76071,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"就是要建立情人都可以进的学校","timestamp":1593751168,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":76367,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":13060,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"生 产 关 系 再 生 产","timestamp":1593755669,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":13060,"reply":7,"tag":"政治相关","text":"旧学校总是说，它要造就知识全面的人，它教的是一般科学。\n\n我们知道，这完全是撒谎，因为过去整个社会赖以生存和维持的基础，就是把人分成阶级，分成剥削者和被压迫者。自然，贯串着阶级精神的旧学校，也就只能向资产阶级的子女传授知识。这种学校里的每一句话，都是根据资产阶级的利益捏造出来的。\n\n工农的年轻一代在这样的学校里，与其说是受教育，不如说是受资产阶级的奴化。\n\n教育这些青年的目的，就是训练对资产阶级有用的奴仆，使之既能替资产阶级创造利润，又不会惊扰资产阶级的安宁和悠闲。","timestamp":1593750507,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782587,"url":"","vote":{}}}